Introduction

Yeonwoo is a South Korean actress, model, and singer under 9ato Entertainment. She was a former member of the girl group MOMOLAND. She used to be an MBK and Pledis trainee before joining the survival show "Finding Momoland"; the show that lead her to debuting as a member of MOMOLAND.

She debuted as a member of MOMOLAND on November 10, 2016 with their first mini album 'Welcome to Momoland'.

On November 30, 2019, MLD Entertainment released a statement saying "While Yeonwoo has had deep affection for her MOMOLAND activities, she has decided that continuing together with her actress activities would be too much strain for both her team and herself so to leave the team and concentrate on her career as our actress [under MLD Entertainment]."

On January 19, 2022, it was announced that she has signed an exclusive contract with 9ato Entertainment.
